    "terms_of_use": "Terms of Use & Privacy",
    "last_update": "Last update: {date}",
    "terms_introduction": "Welcome to the 'Syrian Home' platform. Please read these terms carefully before using the application, as your use of the platform implies your implicit agreement to all the terms listed below.",
    "term1_title": "1. Content and Advertising Responsibility",
    "term1_content": "The user acknowledges that all information entered (prices, areas, photos, licenses) is their personal responsibility. Syrian Home does not guarantee the accuracy of the data provided by users, and the buyer must verify the property on the ground before any financial commitment.",
    "term2_title": "2. Property Licenses and Information",
    "term2_content": "When indicating that a property is 'Licensed', this information is entered directly by the advertiser. The platform does not manually review legal documents, and users must verify official licenses from the relevant authorities before completing any transaction.",
    "term3_title": "3. Financial Transactions and Installments",
    "term3_content": "The platform provides indicative data for installments (down payment, installment, duration). Any financial agreement or installment contract made outside the application is the responsibility of the contracting parties, and the platform does not intervene in the collection of amounts or the settlement of financial disputes.",
    "term4_title": "4. Privacy and Data Protection",
    "term4_content": "We are committed to protecting your personal data (phone number, location). Your geographical location is used only to facilitate the process of searching for properties near you, and your contact data is not shared except with registered users interested in your offers.",
    "term5_title": "5. Specialized Properties",
    "term5_content": "Given the platform's support for diverse properties (farms, warehouses, clinics), the advertiser must specify the correct classification of the property to avoid deleting the ad. It is forbidden to post any property that violates the applicable Syrian laws.",
    "term6_title": "6. Updates and Amendments",
    "term6_content": "The management of the 'Syrian Home' application reserves the right to amend these terms at any time to keep pace with technical and legal developments. Users will be notified of any material changes via the application.",
    "guide_licensed_title": "What does the 'Licensed Property' option mean?",
    "guide_licensed_content": "This option indicates that the property owner stated that the property has all the necessary legal licenses. We always advise you to review the original identification papers during the inspection and before paying any amounts.",
    "guide_installment_title": "How does the installment system work in the app?",
    "guide_installment_content": "Some properties provide an 'Installment' option. You can see the value of the down payment, the monthly installment, and the installment duration directly in the property details if the advertiser has enabled this option.",
    "guide_offline_title": "Does the application work without internet?",
    "guide_offline_content": "Yes! Thanks to caching technology, you can browse the last properties you viewed even if you are out of coverage. A warning sign will appear that you are in 'Offline Mode'.",
    "guide_types_title": "What types of properties does the app support?",
    "guide_types_content": "Our application is comprehensive; it supports apartments, farms (with irrigation and crop details), warehouses, medical clinics, commercial shops, and even rest houses with accurate data for each type.",
    "guide_featured_title": "How do I make my property appear in the 'Featured' section?",
    "guide_featured_content": "Featured properties appear at the top of the home page and get 10 times more views. You can request this service when adding your property to increase the speed of sale.",
    "guide_contact_title": "How do I contact the advertiser?",
    "guide_contact_content": "Inside each property page, you will find quick buttons for calling, or sending a direct WhatsApp message, or via email without having to save the number in your phone.",
